mg.com/50/aed73753d284eeb6c4fde1cb254ffd7e_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/f87bb200ff3fd9059cfe6b7eb3fd5dd0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="687" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/f87bb200ff3fd9059cfe6b7eb3fd5dd0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/22a6e03a9c7e233f331e0b0fe44179d0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="640" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/22a6e03a9c7e233f331e0b0fe44179d0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/fa85ef87d20800084157e9e3ff64612a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1104" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/fa85ef87d20800084157e9e3ff64612a_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/1fa1bef8939f5e6ee7fb441c15991b84_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="449" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/1fa1bef8939f5e6ee7fb441c15991b84_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/8ebff0e01f5eb25a8e631173cfeab5c7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="735" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/8ebff0e01f5eb25a8e631173cfeab5c7_r.jpg"></figure>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p><b>LEMA  </b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.lemamobili.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">lema HOME PAGE </a></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7d72e003f42e78fe04640629739ad966_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="157" data-rawheight="53" class="content_image" width="157"></figure><p>意大利比较全面的家具品牌，成立于1970年，早年涉足全屋定制的业务，因此为多品类的家具都拥有专业的工艺技术。</p><p>LEMA设计能力比较强,产品有拥有独特的气质和设计感。</p><br><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/0588b9dff5b9e2b476c0dfe40515a412_b.jpg" dat