------------------------------------------<br></p><br><p><b>FLEXFORM</b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.flexform.it/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">flexform  HOME</a></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/8cf08fedd36abfc3840d7a7deef33307_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="138" data-rawheight="24" class="content_image" width="138"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0de3ed6cad1e8d6ad3ca99b5ddf57e0d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="486" data-rawheight="658" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="486" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0de3ed6cad1e8d6ad3ca99b5ddf57e0d_r.jpg"></figure><p>Flexform , 专业的沙发品牌，产品没有其他品牌那么宽泛还是主营沙发和座椅。</p><p>之前的沙发都喜欢绷得紧紧的，flexform创造了那种软趴趴的沙发形式，这样一个个电视土豆就从里面舒服得生长出来了。</p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/50dc50b73359a44865c2f78ecba14b17_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="672" data-rawheight="900" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="672" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/50dc50b73359a44865c2f78ecba14b17_r.jpg"></figure>旗下MOOD品牌扩大了产品线，生产内容更丰富一些。<br><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/980eabafd6934af6c776c7867f1c4108_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="552" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/980eabafd6934af6c776c7867f1c4108_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/c386cb1b7d8cd7567478d28dea8dafc8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="464" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/c386cb1b7d8cd7567478d28dea8dafc8_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/5a5d173600304aea5b3c00e3cd0a85c4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1016" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/5a5d173600304aea5b3c00e3cd0a85c4_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/859a506bc9ebd44d147013628bf8ec54_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="791" class="origin_i