tps://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2e74868d6f0f43a527046bbc19376e64_r.jpg"></figure><p>一个专注于座椅方面的意大利品牌。产品主要以沙发，扶手椅，躺椅等为主。材料主要用顶级皮料来加工。</p><p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2aa87df45fbc63e9b5f5c565507f7134_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="552" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2aa87df45fbc63e9b5f5c565507f7134_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/64356bbfedee25c59eddffaccf2174b9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="442" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/64356bbfedee25c59eddffaccf2174b9_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/31ab951c62cd7f937e39468c4f65b8a9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="974" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/31ab951c62cd7f937e39468c4f65b8a9_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/685e1fc5052962aec32d14496d3057e3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="453" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/685e1fc5052962aec32d14496d3057e3_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/50857784dff343f39efd1015d13cec6e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="627" data-rawheight="423" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="627" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/50857784dff343f39efd1015d13cec6e_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/1dcb433a64a351d670eed470ab00362e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="565" data-rawheight="424" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="565" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/1dcb433a64a351d670eed470ab00362e_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/75da5e4278423cf5be2580158e8eeab9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="736" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/75da5e4278423cf5be2580158e8eeab9_r.jpg"></figure><figure>