e><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/fd688750ee70bd27375f66047aab6062_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1103" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/fd688750ee70bd27375f66047aab6062_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/10d488726c6339890b8811b6f0522791_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="690" data-rawheight="460" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="690" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/10d488726c6339890b8811b6f0522791_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/475063aaf4e5173a005d33c3acf5628d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="560" data-rawheight="380" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="560" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/475063aaf4e5173a005d33c3acf5628d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/623f33009ced1760ac63f561a3be4792_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1105" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/623f33009ced1760ac63f561a3be4792_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/446ac3dd810312b8474ba1eac0fd72c0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="521" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/446ac3dd810312b8474ba1eac0fd72c0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/ab7dbf38bc655c68f1cc3aaf83317533_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="552" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/ab7dbf38bc655c68f1cc3aaf83317533_r.jpg"></figure>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</b></p><br><p><b>• </b><b>• </b><b>• </b><b>设计产品品牌</b><b>• </b><b>• </b><b>• </b></p><br><p><b>相比于之前的大品牌家具，设计品品牌没那么注重套房和成套系列的设计，更加关注单品，产品更具时尚和经典。</b></p><br><p>Moroso  <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.moroso.it/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">The beauty of design				 :			Moroso</a></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7aca8d0384a46379fe9270d1ae128991_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="218" data-rawheight="49" class="content_image" width="218"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/3c7827f4c3f22e347ffba836c995f9e9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="475" class="content_image" width="400"></figure><p>成立于1952年，意大利著名时尚家具品牌，签约超过70位顶级设计师，拥有无数件经典产品。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/7d969d7bd8086690d3739bc227a21475_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1369" data-rawheight="1060" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1369" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/7d969d7bd8086690d3739bc227a21475_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/57ccb1f62416cb4296d8cad2cf2bf747_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="946" data-rawheight="1105" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="946" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/57ccb1f62416cb4296d8cad2cf2bf747_r.jpg"></figure><br><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/75d3fef03edd8191d7db77fdea4cbf67_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="368" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/75d3fef03edd8191d7db77fdea4cbf67_r.jpg"></figure><br><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/49e86e35c10e4be6b33772ebaf6eb260_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="918" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/49e86e35c10e4be6b33772ebaf6eb260_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/8d264ab2d5070e5d343e6e735f6fe23e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="490" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/8d264ab2d5070e5d343e6e735f6fe23e_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/8cc0d155e41b3e5cddb55ca49fdad357_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="520" data-rawheight="421" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="520" data-original="htt