---------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><p><b>Vitra</b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.vitra.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">vitra.com </a></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/719ceb1ae6db74655f76cfa067e37176_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="110" data-rawheight="44" class="content_image" width="110"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/bae3879dae0ad6485ea22f5a8a439296_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="551" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/bae3879dae0ad6485ea22f5a8a439296_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b>VITRA是第一家拥有家具设计博物馆的德国家具品牌，缘于他们对设计师的重视，同样合作的设计师们也为Vitra带来了可以持续创造无限价值的经典产品。Eames夫妇大部分的设计作品都是与Vitra合作的。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/cb58d2628ecd05e1b03b423502ee330f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="950" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/cb58d2628ecd05e1b03b423502ee330f_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/0f97f651ba8f1dd1bcbeb98ca913c3e8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="666" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/0f97f651ba8f1dd1bcbeb98ca913c3e8_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/24ed33e1dddcead2eceffd92f4a0262a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="545" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/24ed33e1dddcead2eceffd92f4a0262a_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/65419737c080331e03d389673e5df69b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="525" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/65419737c080331e03d389673e5df69b_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/f11f4fb2b19b7a86729b36c2fce6bd83_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="944" class="origin_