.com/?target=http%3A//www.kartell.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Kartell – Made in Italy design</a></b></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/3919e9c252ed057c10924a99b3a9c897_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="141" data-rawheight="52" class="content_image" width="141"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/33589b816e080c7d447909db34f9b496_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="500" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/33589b816e080c7d447909db34f9b496_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>1949年创立，曾被评为最具创意公司。以塑料家具闻名于世，带动了全球对塑料家具新的认识和潮流。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c1c97092a836e401da4ab525342b665c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="750" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c1c97092a836e401da4ab525342b665c_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/acd9fe7ab298f45b774bb3b1a2c0acde_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="493" data-rawheight="740" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="493" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/acd9fe7ab298f45b774bb3b1a2c0acde_r.jpg"></figure><br><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/69e2bf2936a811633d805fcaf20eb9e6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="333" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image" width="333"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/97716559b27ad340057c384ea58ca034_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="333" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image" width="333"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2730f0172d909861ed30e4662432a2e2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="981" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2730f0172d909861ed30e4662432a2e2_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c0b2010aaeab3d8b0933d2712d7baaac_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1106" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c0b2010aaeab3d8b0933d2712d7baaac_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/99e97bef26cedc708c9f3e311625a8a2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="467" data-rawheight="700" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="467" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/99e97bef26cedc708c9f3e311625a8a2_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/e55fccd48112292276886150953c7fa9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/e55fccd48112292276886150953c7fa9_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/38c4a36965e980365225a2fc5fde0b27_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1068" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/38c4a36965e980365225a2fc5fde0b27_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/6f088c94d5b65d37d354aead4ecb56ce_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="963" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/6f088c94d5b65d37d354aead4ecb56ce_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b>中国演员刘孜，曾经在北京开设了kartell的代理销售公司。现在想必也没那么滋润吧，这是所有大牌家具到了国内遇到的普遍问题。</b></p><p> ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p><b>Magis   </b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.magisdesign.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">www.magisdesign.com</a></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/db26427fbaa382c8c505ea4b81e01311_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="80" data-rawheight="78" class="content_image" width="80"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/150fc9f07909b03571347750f7ba6ec7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="645" data-rawheight="862" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="645" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/150fc9f07909b03571347750f7ba6ec7_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b>1976年成立。个人非常喜欢的家具品牌，也是以塑料家具闻名，转为探索更高科技的合成材料的研发。</b></p><br><p><b>品牌调性也十分另类，造型活泼，理念前卫，有独特的生活趣味。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/68b4899d7d0d683514ebc3553e909322_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="584" data-rawheight="779" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="584" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/68b4899d7d0d683514ebc3553e909322_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/4cf539922fbc142e88a2e43174dc5f7a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="533" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="533" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/4cf539922fbc142e88a2e43174dc5f7a_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/47bedfc86ee44f61fad3c00c5ed3a6d1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="600" class="content_image" width="400"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/75f21f556f62797ce5a0c6b0422ee9f1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="579" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/75f21f556f62797ce5a0c6b0422ee9f1_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7e61f78dce5893f54baa475bd34eb8a4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7e61f78dce5893f54baa475bd34eb8a4_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/a0b482b08e4d512d1f213cf08eaf0b49_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="468" data-rawheight="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="468" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/a0b482b08e4d512d1f213cf08eaf0b49_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/f60a58adea15a13148b520b305635607_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="714" data-rawheight="952" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="714" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/f60a58adea15a13148b520b305635607_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/784fd809ba716ada6c44d82ce3c8726c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="472" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="472" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/784fd809ba716ada6c44d82ce3c8726c_r.jpg"></figure><p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/b38d16aeb7c871d273e2077191b51a70_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/b38d16aeb7c871d273e2077191b51a70_r.jpg"></figure>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><p><b>                                               • </b><b>• </b><b>• 北欧风格</b><b>品牌</b><b>• </b><b>• </b><b>• </b><br></p><br><br><p><b>Artek   <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.artek.fi/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Artek</a></b></p><p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/e639822f855cc0cea52d233d9941a116_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="129" data-rawheight="50" class="content_image" width="129"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2d0636c7f75375d218e203efea922ee8_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="640" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2d0636c7f75375d218e203efea922ee8_r.jpg"></figure><b>Artek 是由著名家具设计师Alver Aalto 1935年创立于芬兰。Artek 朝着自然与建筑思维的延展为设计家俱的依据，展现北欧风情简朴、民主化的北欧风格设计。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/48f7905e7b3f7f9941bbd485fe677c56_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="625" data-rawheight="640" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="625" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/48f7905e7b3f7f9941bbd485fe677c56_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/bb163113a77eb43fba0c50c7c526647a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="395" data-rawheight="554" class="content_image" width="395"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/a46723221e5f234ba3f710c63d4b615b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="500" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/a46723221e5f234ba3f710c63d4b615b_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/fd2a63b764150cbbe4c8ec71b9e65310_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="441" data-rawheight="549" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="441" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/fd2a63b764150cbbe4c8ec71b9e65310_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c7908bc208f2bef8c651da8300b5f0df_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="499" data-rawheight="665" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="499" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c7908bc208f2bef8c651da8300b5f0df_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/72aa4ccf5c7b591a8aadf3d54b63c2ae_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="390" data-rawheight="586" class="content_image" width="390"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/0fa53c2ab960d5e299a82c742894fc4a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="743" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/0fa53c2ab960d5e299a82c742894fc4a_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dbfd470613c8d6e8244ec98a8891c00b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="700" data-rawheight="570" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="700" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dbfd470613c8d6e8244ec98a8891c00b_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/d0274d75ac4d350036d29d02efc9dd6b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="552" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/d0274d75ac4d350036d29d02efc9dd6b_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/f41051e04ab783902f78a31468ca303d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1104" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/f41051e04ab783902f78a31468ca303d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/b137e747dddd72020de94720c0c41b13_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="600" class="content_image" width="400"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dad97f98928045cece7b23a1c0fd7653_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="559" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dad97f98928045cece7b23a1c0fd7653_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/266950f710cdec1a338017354a746985_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/266950f710cdec1a338017354a746985_r.jpg"></figure><p> -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p><b>Fritz Hansen  </b><b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.fritzhansen.com/en/fritz-hansen" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Fritz Hansen</a></b></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/c9544984dbf9918f0487d2e8d6c06248_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="172" data-rawheight="41" class="content_image" width="172"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/e79662bc5215de31250084c4ce7f949d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="534" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="534" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/e79662bc5215de31250084c4ce7f949d_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>创立于丹麦的1872年的经典家具品牌，设计大师Arne Jacobsen为该企业设计了大量传世的经典作品，也奠定了品牌的产品设计原则：</b></p><br><p><b>原创(Original) 不盲目追随流行的独特原创设计</b></p><p><b>纯净 (Pure) 形随功能的简约美学</b></p><p><b>工艺(Sculptural) 精雕细琢的形体美感与工艺品质</b></p><p><b>恒久(Timeless) 可经得起时间考验的经典美学设计</b></p><p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/05ec0addbdb2c0a96f5533fc9070f1db_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="530" data-rawheight="657" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="530" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/05ec0addbdb2c0a96f5533fc9070f1db_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/8aa157262b4aead69881a53bbe98fd80_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="390" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/8aa157262b4aead69881a53bbe98fd80_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/171bad20c772e57b5e8a17b5b5076f85_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="534" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="534" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/171bad20c772e57b5e8a17b5b5076f85_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/21eb2727dac4ddafa322f2182f84840d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="590" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/21eb2727dac4ddafa322f2182f84840d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dde1ed542046b46e1d6fec8af671911d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="652" data-rawheight="850" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="652" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dde1ed542046b46e1d6fec8af671911d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/39af810b12106a998bc11ac16a5ad9b1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="736" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/39af810b12106a998bc11ac16a5ad9b1_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/4831be63935ce99e52bb0f7e16809782_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="468" data-rawheight="468" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="468" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/4831be63935ce99e52bb0f7e16809782_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/cf59e00d0f501eb18f852a8c6904958e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="954" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/cf59e00d0f501eb18f852a8c6904958e_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/153d17333be9ef36e5531f7f49b2abf0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="679" data-rawheight="1000" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="679" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/153d17333be9ef36e5531f7f49b2abf0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/8be6b1b26a1cb81410e59fabe37c2f72_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="383" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/8be6b1b26a1cb81410e59fabe37c2f72_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/eb0e76c9e380a949fb4f738eac2c6cdf_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="276" data-rawheight="500" class="content_image" width="276"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/c13f37cc1cb0a943b328998cd021a872_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="640" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/c13f37cc1cb0a943b328998cd021a872_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/781e68934c4c0bcdeac232525df9ac31_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="592" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/781e68934c4c0bcdeac232525df9ac31_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/00c2d5c230cb44b0372ae2edf7bd7cf1_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="478" data-rawheight="598" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="478" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/00c2d5c230cb44b0372ae2edf7bd7cf1_r.jpg"></figure>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><p><b>Carl hansen &amp;son  <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.carlhansen.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Carl Hansen &amp; Søn</a></b></p><br><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/b2c6a3aa5594e1b0a474c29079d62839_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="640" data-rawheight="960" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="640" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/b2c6a3aa5594e1b0a474c29079d62839_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>1908年成立，总部设立在丹麦的Aarup。但一直是一家小公司啊，做了20多年，稍微有一点点规模，开始跟一些设计师合作。但是发展还是缓慢啊，规模也没啥变化。</b></p><p><b>直到，1949年跟设计师 汉斯·魏格纳合作，出了一把 Y chair 后，魏格纳越战越勇，出了一大波后来闻名于世的家具。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/db7ce5d949346fed2bbb1d0bef507512_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="714" data-rawheight="1013" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="714" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/db7ce5d949346fed2bbb1d0bef507512_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/aea19c9ceea60771b7b59f254c0c55e9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="649" data-rawheight="309" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="649" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/aea19c9ceea60771b7b59f254c0c55e9_r.jpg"></figure><br><br><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/aa97316d2f2e9a80d023b54105e75416_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="903" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/aa97316d2f2e9a80d023b54105e75416_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7374ec24e105afe88a73a31f78224dc9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="464" data-rawheight="700" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="464" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/7374ec24e105afe88a73a31f78224dc9_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/b00ab8b7e65f6e0f95ecef9dc992fff5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="630" data-rawheight="420" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="630" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/b00ab8b7e65f6e0f95ecef9dc992fff5_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/d0337b66beccc8a25f250cd2aabe8f50_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="709" data-rawheight="1064" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="709" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/d0337b66beccc8a25f250cd2aabe8f50_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/d3ac63043b7e2ce51295fb70259d71c4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="540" data-rawheight="810" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="540" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/d3ac63043b7e2ce51295fb70259d71c4_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2d040320c320e609054dc5a89db01449_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="750" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2d040320c320e609054dc5a89db01449_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/a39a9e6daab6793df5b2c5555e367ac7_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="482" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/a39a9e6daab6793df5b2c5555e367ac7_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/30da91d267820d27e46f13b190d2b10b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="630" data-rawheight="420" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="630" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/30da91d267820d27e46f13b190d2b10b_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/23a4bd56dafb979b8bc82b363093d888_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="468" data-rawheight="702" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="468" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/23a4bd56dafb979b8bc82b363093d888_r.jpg"></figure>直到今天，carl hansen&amp;son 主要就是依靠卖汉斯·魏格纳的产品，而且每年啥事不用干，把汉斯的椅子换个新色系，找个平面设计师再出出布料图案，分分钟又能刷到销售榜前面去，真是捡了大宝啊！</b><br></p><p> -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><br><p><b>IKEA</b></p><p><b>这个不用多做介绍。</b></p><br><br><br><p> -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p><b>                                                    • </b><b>• </b><b>• 办公家具</b><b>品牌</b><b>• </b><b>• </b><b>• </b></p><br><p><b>Martela</b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.martela.fi/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">martela.fi/</span><span class="invisible"></span></a></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3dcb1f0487d595475dc8a08282e7481c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="113" data-rawheight="114" class="content_image" width="113"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/9bebebad9f40e1831d3883571c5ac272_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="451" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/9bebebad9f40e1831d3883571c5ac272_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>Martela是成立于芬兰，非常受欢迎的国际办公家具品牌。但是家具风格时尚前卫，有着北欧四国骨子里nordic的风格特点，颜色丰富，造型自然简约。<br></b></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3d997d053f5c54078b86e0ed60c29a60_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="900" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3d997d053f5c54078b86e0ed60c29a60_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/49b63890eb5c12d245b2e4f251771e7c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="590" data-rawheight="800" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="590" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/49b63890eb5c12d245b2e4f251771e7c_r.jpg"></figure><br><br><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/067d4e79ce8240dc32f3638e2b64d4b4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="1108" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/067d4e79ce8240dc32f3638e2b64d4b4_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/70c2389782f374c505f38f7c79f72991_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="450" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/70c2389782f374c505f38f7c79f72991_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/1f15621471b1f24ee432275edac1baae_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="500" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/1f15621471b1f24ee432275edac1baae_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/ebdea2da0c158b1d6190c4135bc4bb6c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="552" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/ebdea2da0c158b1d6190c4135bc4bb6c_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/b5fbfe975014c2297164693192b8bcaf_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="853" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-th