00" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/2627a6c83872347f190d835311dce724_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b>可惜在国内不好买，否则肯定会被新型的互联网企业追捧，看看Google，Facebook的办公室就知道必然深受喜欢。</b></p><p>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><p>Herman miller   <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.hermanmiller.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Furniture - Herman Miller</a><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//store.hermanmiller.cn/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://</span><span class="visible">store.hermanmiller.cn/</span><span class="invisible"></span></a></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/6dfb0b0a562c7e2b96d4265b83149a84_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="232" data-rawheight="61" class="content_image" width="232"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/779bdc82e57178ff489f98d660dc95a4_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="920" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/779bdc82e57178ff489f98d660dc95a4_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>美国的大型办公家具品牌，到底是美国品牌，跟中国人总是走得很近，不像欧洲品牌藏着掖着。早早就在国内开起了销售店，现在都有了网上商城，可以直接购买。</b></p><p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/841ce6588dabd713772ba4dd8026adaf_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="683" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/841ce6588dabd713772ba4dd8026adaf_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/39a07bc85511a55c1934387b80812dc6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="391" data-rawheight="489" class="content_image" width="391"></figure>AERON 比起其他看起来炫酷的，还是推荐这款。好用。</p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/67dbe30e087347b7af25893799c770be_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="680" data-rawheight="429" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="680" data-original="https://pic1.zhim