></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/5f5fc75dacd88ff50cedbd5021454cbc_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="566" data-rawheight="725" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="566" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/5f5fc75dacd88ff50cedbd5021454cbc_r.jpg"></figure>-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><br><p><b>Steelcase</b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.steelcase.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Steelcase - Office Furniture Solutions, Education &amp; Healthcare Furniture</a></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/b60614b809bb1321937701beb8dfa176_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="170" data-rawheight="50" class="content_image" width="170"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/46d06c7b17c5bdbde72893a99552093e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="450" data-rawheight="600" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="450" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/46d06c7b17c5bdbde72893a99552093e_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>1912年创立的美国办公家具品牌，是办公家具行业的老大哥。但是产品设计和理念一点不老，引领了办公家具行业的各种创新变革。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0706897aa194c046da38c5273f662b4f_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="412" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0706897aa194c046da38c5273f662b4f_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/82b53e3034a6f45ea33a4cff68547aac_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="620" data-rawheight="393" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="620" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/82b53e3034a6f45ea33a4cff68547aac_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/29a161889c75c24c31531a0ab02ee8e6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="412" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/29a161889c75c24c31531a0ab02ee8e6_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/8c1fc0584ffabce98f1e2927c1c6f8bb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="545" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/8c1fc0584ffabce98f1e2927c1c6f8bb_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b>相对于HM或者contessa等品牌，steelcase更注重办公家具体系和工作环境理念的创立。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/221b8ba685d9a3515512d3271c4e72ef_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="320" data-rawheight="480" class="content_image" width="320"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c663d03d0baae0413603113cc9b1ac4c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="580" data-rawheight="400" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="580" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c663d03d0baae0413603113cc9b1ac4c_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/0c8a1061ecaa1b28aa59f2daf57ac6d2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="400" data-rawheight="600" class="content_image" width="400"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/062731026003c8c299fdc23b6cb9b937_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="463" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/062731026003c8c299fdc23b6cb9b937_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/f58c5c69e8b6de0eb27724d87e21c4b0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="952" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/f58c5c69e8b6de0eb27724d87e21c4b0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/0be795f852b5a4fe78793233ce02e135_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="400" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/0be795f852b5a4fe78793233ce02e135_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/38fa060d451685129b6df231a5d06721_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="414" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/38fa060d451685129b6df231a5d06721_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/954c3809afe60335cbccc3ef55100e8b_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="552" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/954c3809afe60335cbccc3ef55100e8b_r.jpg"></figure><p>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p><b>   • </b><b>• </b><b>• 其他家具</b><b>品牌</b><b>• </b><b>• </b><b>• </b></p><br><p>Bassett  <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.bassettfurniture.com/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Bassett Furniture</a></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/6255acbd2f8e6922f70c26d7ce53c668_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="221" data-rawheight="65" class="content_image" width="221"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/c24c80c28c84cf9cad1207b41f75dcdb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/c24c80c28c84cf9cad1207b41f75dcdb_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>一个美国本土的美式家具品牌。虽然这类设计风格在国际范围内并不是那么受欢迎，但是在美国还是火的。一看有点哥伦布登陆带过来顺带跟印第安人组合出来的美国乡村风格，在美国也叫传统家具啊。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/3bca705b7d5e53a5473adfce4cdbd8fa_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/3bca705b7d5e53a5473adfce4cdbd8fa_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/635874834e85048a56fcc298c4a0368d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/635874834e85048a56fcc298c4a0368d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/b30dec5c7d0e6be8551f03db29cf49ba_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="565" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/b30dec5c7d0e6be8551f03db29cf49ba_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/1ee51141bd9ccdd14d39634a56f6f123_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="480" data-rawheight="480" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="480" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/1ee51141bd9ccdd14d39634a56f6f123_r.jpg"></figure>---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br><p><b>Halo  </b><b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.halo-nz.co.nz/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">Home | Halo Furniture</a></b></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/6e89ef00e4a3cc74637e72a5023cd472_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="362" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/6e89ef00e4a3cc74637e72a5023cd472_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>这个就算是英国的传统家具品牌了，体量不算大，但是好像挺收欢迎，可能产品气质比较独特把。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/1b4bf9f57180a6fcdb19799dc3f5bb2d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="441" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/1b4bf9f57180a6fcdb19799dc3f5bb2d_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/33946b1d855fa11de19873730a341c46_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="577" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/33946b1d855fa11de19873730a341c46_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2aa0bf365a89bda44ced4947ba889038_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="707" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/2aa0bf365a89bda44ced4947ba889038_r.jpg"></figure><br><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/d19b00306720ff930ec05fcdfbeb4f71_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="404" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/d19b00306720ff930ec05fcdfbeb4f71_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/a43139f3c71ea910c2c3cd3df174e51e_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="340" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/a43139f3c71ea910c2c3cd3df174e51e_r.jpg"></figure><p>--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><p><b>  Hulsta  <a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.huelsta.de/" class=" external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer"><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="visible">huelsta.de/</span><span class="invisible"></span></a></b></p><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/ff80d049ab90cb58ead463394eb7decc_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="135" data-rawheight="35" class="content_image" width="135"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/5ae3aa671351455168c5e18e9ffa35d2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="508" data-rawheight="373" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="508" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/5ae3aa671351455168c5e18e9ffa35d2_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>包豪斯设计理念比较明显的德国家具品牌，产品偏中端，注重材质五金的搭配，大都以套房系列设计为主。</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/9784532985e0a98b6b728f153a7a68f3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="520" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/9784532985e0a98b6b728f153a7a68f3_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/83584f52c10964842949fe45ca86d3c0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="736" data-rawheight="487" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="736" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/83584f52c10964842949fe45ca86d3c0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0421dfe9da2263b647e114b560d25d59_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="625" data-rawheight="625" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="625" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/0421dfe9da2263b647e114b560d25d59_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/362b5c494f1e602515faf2b32a9adf78_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="490" data-rawheight="352" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="490" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/362b5c494f1e602515faf2b32a9adf78_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c34c7e74350211cccd3e800530b5e3d0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="570" data-rawheight="409" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="570" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/c34c7e74350211cccd3e800530b5e3d0_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/383a8db1a14335ef2223621ece08562a_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="638" data-rawheight="409" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="638" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/383a8db1a14335ef2223621ece08562a_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3a1093457668037bfe58221072768dd9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="430" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3a1093457668037bfe58221072768dd9_r.jpg"></figure><p><b>比较符合国人买家具的理念 ，所有国内品牌 “某强”多年一直在像素级的仿造。如果了解国内家具品牌的一看就懂。</b></p><p> ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------</p><br><p><b> DEDON   </b><b><a href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//www.dedon.de/" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">DEDON: Homepage</a></b></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/dc1cfe8d28d153ef7a8d0942c7a8e190_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="101" data-rawheight="50" class="content_image" width="101"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/3cb55f61381b3a138c31ff518c4c39fb_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="600" data-rawheight="449" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="600" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/3cb55f61381b3a138c31ff518c4c39fb_r.jpg"></figure><br><p><b>Dedon 在户外家具里可谓享誉盛名，至少在户外家具的产品设计领域已经只手遮天了，各种奇思妙想，天马行空都能被创造出来，而户外家具的设计正离不开这点。</b></p><p><b><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/cc72777bb55b405d96b23585aaee4215_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="554" data-rawheight="640" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="554" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/cc72777bb55b405d96b23585aaee4215_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/71b56342c4ba698b1e38b82b33e084db_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="500" data-rawheight="672" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="500" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/71b56342c4ba698b1e38b82b33e084db_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/bb5893bd9c046b10c2f7c8f5030d5d5c_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="444" data-rawheight="624" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="444" data-original="https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/bb5893bd9c046b10c2f7c8f5030d5d5c_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/28b54d90501f6abd748f36b119c2d2e3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="464" data-rawheight="550" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="464" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/28b54d90501f6abd748f36b119c2d2e3_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2179b31bcb39d1db37f8974542a39f34_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="513" data-rawheight="768" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="513" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/2179b31bcb39d1db37f8974542a39f34_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3dce6f6e54188c6ec21efa78de7536b5_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="433" data-rawheight="578" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="433" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/3dce6f6e54188c6ec21efa78de7536b5_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/b8582ec68749db3d32a9fef51ebb2455_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="715" data-rawheight="472" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="715" data-original="https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/b8582ec68749db3d32a9fef51ebb2455_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/8734c60a345d310ac0192aaa671138a6_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="570" data-rawheight="994" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="570" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/8734c60a345d310ac0192aaa671138a6_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/ebbb6d1cdf006e0304b2eb9ae0c652f2_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="673" data-rawheight="557" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="673" data-original="https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/ebbb6d1cdf006e0304b2eb9ae0c652f2_r.jpg"></figure><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/555770a21a833b0425764443abd5d2e9_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="431" data-rawheight="578" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="431" data-original="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/555770a21a833b0425764443abd5d2e9_r.jpg"></figure>最后一张来点点福利。</b></p><p><b>-------------------------------------------------正文完-----------------------------------------------------</b></p><br><p><b>整理得脑子都胀了，肯定多多少少有漏缺的品牌，希望知友能提醒，谢谢。</b></p><br><p><b>最后再贴一下知乎专栏：<a href="http://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/morethan" class="internal">木上 - 知乎专栏</a></b></p><p><b>微信公众号：                 morethanwood</b></p><figure><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/71f92978283e7e84d704a7ea8f9658b0_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="344" data-rawheight="344" data-tag="qrcode" data-qrvalue="http://weixin.qq.com/r/7jv44LLEbO8TrfaD9278" class="content_image" width="344"></figure></script><a class="time" href="/question/31181577/answer/51610225">2015-06-17</a></div></div></div></article><div class="item-footer js-contentActions"><ul class="item-actions"><li class="hidden-tablet hidden-desktop"><button class="button-text vote-num js-openVoteDialog"><span data-bind-votecount>4015</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text follow unfollowing" data-follow="q:fi:button" data-id="4655255"><i class="fi fi-follow"></i><span class="label">关注</span></button></li><li><button class="button-text comment js-toggleCommentBox toggle-comment"><i class="fi fi-comment"></i><span class="label">228 条评论</span></button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-thank "><i class="fi fi-thank"></i>感谢</button></li><li class="hidden-phone"><button class="button-text auto-hide js-share"><i class="fi fi-share"></i>分享</but