b129_l.jpg" class="avatar d50" alt="王通"></img></a><div class="content"><a href="/roundtable/haojiaju/wang-tong-77-64/answers" class="answers text-muted">5 个回答</a><a class="name author-link" href="/people/wang-tong-77-64" data-hovercard='p$t$wang-tong-77-64'>王通</a><span class="icon icon-badge-identity icon-badge" data-tooltip="s$b$已认证的个人"></span><div class="bio">集祥家居 品牌联合创始人暨首席设计师</div></div></div></li></ul></div></div><div class="module participants"><div class="module-header"><h3>热门回答者</h3></div><div class="module-body"><ul class="items-fulid"><li class="item"><a href="/people/homeupgrade" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$homeupgrade'><img src="https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a3f9b237225eb1965a8f6024ca4984a7_l.jpg" alt="菠萝斑马" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/org/shen-me-zhi-de-mai-76-83" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$shen-me-zhi-de-mai-76-83'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-84d07c1b8e1e14d7d4598b0ea4c02ce0_l.jpg" alt="什么值得买" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/LandHome" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$LandHome'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/70a8c9c092901815ffd2ec12e6f0fc40_l.jpg" alt="陈军" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/xiao-xin-hui-lai-la" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$xiao-xin-hui-lai-la'><img src="https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-3282c6083d5ff1357eccea210716e933_l.jpg" alt="我回来啦" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/yi-qu-er-san-li-10" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$yi-qu-er-san-li-10'><img src="https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b220cf3243138f465e1652b13bbc7378_l.jpg" alt="一去二三里" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/mu-jiang-xiao-qiang" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$mu-jiang-xiao-qiang'><img src="https://pic4.zhimg.com/9832aec74b9ee8e2c86c996d0e8e7ce8_l.jpg" alt="木匠小强" class="avatar d50"></a></li><li class="item"><a href="/people/mononoke" class="item-link" data-hovercard='p$t$mononoke'><img src="https://pic2